net.doo.snap.mrzscanner

Class MRZScannerFrameHandler

  • net.doo.snap.mrzscanner.MRZScannerFrameHandler

  • public class MRZScannerFrameHandler

    Performs MRZ data detection on camera preview frames. Outputs results via interface MRZScannerFrameHandler.ResultHandler (net.doo.snap.mrzscanner.MRZScannerFrameHandler$addResultHandler(net.doo.snap.mrzscanner.MRZScannerFrameHandler.ResultHandler)).

    Preview frame considered intercepted if at least one interface MRZScannerFrameHandler.ResultHandler returns true from io.scanbot.sdk.camera.BaseResultHandler$handle(io.scanbot.sdk.camera.FrameHandlerResult)

    See Also:

      • addResultHandler

        public void addResultHandler(net.doo.snap.mrzscanner.MRZScannerFrameHandler.ResultHandler handler)

        Registers result handler which will be notified about MRZ data detection results.

        Results are coming on the worker thread. Don't forget to move execution to main thread before updating UI.

        Parameters:
        handler - handler to register. Must not be null. If handler was already registered, nothing happens.

      • removeResultHandler

        public void removeResultHandler(net.doo.snap.mrzscanner.MRZScannerFrameHandler.ResultHandler handler)

        Unregisters handler.

        Parameters:
        handler - handler to unregister. If it was not registered before, nothing happens.
